\'91Hannibal, where I finally understood how much this area means to you. Your father\'92s house \'96confronting the man who hurt you so much. Your mother\'92s house, which is now Go\'92s house, the two people who made you such a good man. But \'85 I guess it doesn\'92t surprise me that you\'92d like to share those places with someone you\'92 \'96 she bowed her head \'96 \'91had fallen in love with. You always liked repeats.\'92\
